Actually NPC's will only chase you onto the boat in OOT if I remember correctly... <P>All other zones where an NPC is chasing you, getting on the boat will cause them to cease pursuit (but not change aggro status).<P>I think that this was instituted to discourage people from using the boats as a way to escape a hopeless situtation, especially in the OOT zone where higher level NPCs are...<P>------------------<BR>Blackivar Backbiter<BR>aka Blackivar the Cunning<BR>Halfling Rogue<BR>21st Season<BR>Druzzil Ro Server
