Early on in the game.. way way back within the first few months.. I was crossing from Erudin to Queynos via boat.  This HUGE and I mean REALLY HUGE shark the size of the boat pops up on the deck randomly.. jaw chomping.  Unfortunately a noob (we were all noobs back then) was between his teeth.. crunch, crunch, dead.  He didn't live too long.  It scared the heck out of me, and I figured I was next.. luckly the shark just sat on the deck of the boat for a while and then popped off to never never land.  I zoned and was luckily spared.
